snippet.title: Ragnarock - Sabaton RAID Content Reveal
snippet.description:
Are you ready for battle with this new Sabaton RAID? 
This new DLC for the Rhythm game Ragnarock brings you a unique collaboration with the epic band Sabaton.

Available on June 22nd !

Get Ragnarock here:
Meta Quest: https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/3749621795127676/
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1345820/Ragnarock/
PSVR2: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/product/UP7137-PPSA14248_00-0492146559940438
Viveport: https://www.viveport.com/89026a8b-5b99-46c0-93dd-13a4c4b4ffc3
And now on Pico! 

Thank you so much for all the support and feedback you give us every day!
WanadevStudio's social accounts are also great spots to share your feelings with us.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/RagnarockVR
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/wanadevstudio/
Discord: https://discord.gg/kVq4sXS
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100063962403745
Our website: https://www.ragnarock-vr.com

#vr #meta #steam #gameplay #gaming  #metaquest2 #meta #rythm_games #ragnarock #metal #psvr
